On Friday 21 March 2025, I had the tom yum egg fried rice with shrimp for my lunch at the brand new Bukit Batok West hawker centre, and I liked this meal as tom yum egg fried rice with shrimp tasted very delicious. Overall, the service provided to me was very good and I would love to try these other wok fried rice dishes (except for pork chop and pork luncheon meat) from this outlet in the future.
Ordered Tom yum pork chop fried rice they gave me normal fried rice and the pork chop only has colour on one side??

The rice was overly dry, lacks flavour and not oily at all. It was also barely seasoned.

The pork chop was on the tougher side.
